<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 14:06:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“以色列-巴勒斯坦阵亡将士纪念日仪式展示了加沙战争后的第二天会是什么样子”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-12/ty-article-podcast/israeli-palestinian-memorial-shows-what-the-day-after-the-gaza-war-could-look-like/0000018f-6ca5-d284-adaf-7cfd64740000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 13:53:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-05-12/ty-article-podcast/israeli-palestinian-memorial-shows-what-the-day-after-the-gaza-war-could-look-like/0000018f-6ca5-d284-adaf-7cfd64740000</guid></item><item><title>身份不明的肇事者纵火焚烧约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦空房子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-empty-house-in-west-bank-set-on-fire-by-unknown-perpetrators/0000018f-6cac-d5b5-a18f-efecabef0000</link><description>房子的墙壁上贴满了标语：“Tag mehir [“价格标签”]——本雅明去世 30 天”，标志着居住在附近定居点的 14 岁以色列男孩本雅明·阿希梅尔 (Binyamin Ahimeir) 被谋杀 30 天。</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 13:51:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-empty-house-in-west-bank-set-on-fire-by-unknown-perpetrators/0000018f-6cac-d5b5-a18f-efecabef0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登并没有背弃以色列。但内塔尼亚胡已经</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/biden-has-not-turned-his-back-on-israel-but-netanyahu-has/0000018f-6bea-d4be-abcf-6bef0bd80000</link><description>几乎从加沙战争一开始，内塔尼亚胡政府就不仅与哈马斯对抗，还与美国总统对抗。将拜登推向崩溃可能会对本已紧张的美以关系造成不可挽回的损害</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 13:01:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/biden-has-not-turned-his-back-on-israel-but-netanyahu-has/0000018f-6bea-d4be-abcf-6bef0bd80000</guid></item><item><title>在战争中，我们失去亲人的以色列人和巴勒斯坦人一起哀悼</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/amid-war-we-bereaved-israelis-and-palestinians-are-mourning-together/0000018f-6bb3-d0ae-adef-ebff29c40000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以色列人的生命被恐怖吞没以来，这对加沙巴勒斯坦人来说是一场尚未结束的灾难，我们来自冲突双方失去亲人的家庭聚集在一起，纪念那些无辜的孩子，他们唯一的罪行就是巴勒斯坦或以色列人</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 12:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/amid-war-we-bereaved-israelis-and-palestinians-are-mourning-together/0000018f-6bb3-d0ae-adef-ebff29c40000</guid></item><item><title>一本关于内塔尼亚胡与哈马斯关系的令人不安的新书</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/a-disturbing-new-book-about-netanyahus-relationship-with-hamas/0000018f-5de2-d65e-a9cf-dfe222de0000</link><description>作家亚当·拉兹 (Adam Raz) 解释了一次与母亲的争吵如何促使他写下《通向 10 月 7 日之路》。另外，贝埃里基布兹艺术画廊在特拉维夫临时住所的苦乐参半的开幕，以及海法酷儿历史节的活动</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 12:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/a-disturbing-new-book-about-netanyahus-relationship-with-hamas/0000018f-5de2-d65e-a9cf-dfe222de0000</guid></item><item><title>“我在特拉维夫见过服务员，他们的英语比以色列外交官更好”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/ive-met-waiters-in-tel-aviv-who-have-a-better-command-of-english-than-israeli-diplomats/0000018f-6c36-d284-adaf-7c7e01570000</link><description>英国记者兼分析师汤姆·格罗斯表示，以色列处于聚光灯下，但其政府未能采取有效的公共外交行动来应对</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 11:41:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/ive-met-waiters-in-tel-aviv-who-have-a-better-command-of-english-than-israeli-diplomats/0000018f-6c36-d284-adaf-7c7e01570000</guid></item><item><title>一名加沙高级医生在以色列拘留期间死亡。官员拒绝解释如何</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/a-senior-gazan-doctor-died-during-israeli-detention-officials-refuse-to-explain-how/0000018f-6c31-d0ae-adef-edfdd51a0000</link><description>阿德南·阿尔-伯什医生去年 12 月在加沙地带的一家医院被捕，四个月后悄然宣布他在以色列监狱死亡。见过他的巴勒斯坦被拘留者表示，很明显他经历了地狱，但以色列军队和监狱部门拒绝透露任何细节</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 10:19:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/a-senior-gazan-doctor-died-during-israeli-detention-officials-refuse-to-explain-how/0000018f-6c31-d0ae-adef-edfdd51a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列独立日赎罪日的演变故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/the-evolving-story-of-yom-haatzmaut-israels-independence-day/0000018f-6bbf-d284-adaf-7fffc6ef0000</link><description>从游行到聚会，从篝火到烧烤，自 1948 年以色列独立以来，其国庆节就像这个国家本身一样在不断变化</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 09:28:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/the-evolving-story-of-yom-haatzmaut-israels-independence-day/0000018f-6bbf-d284-adaf-7fffc6ef0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列将在加沙战争中纪念阵亡将士纪念日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-memorial-day-kicks-off-amid-war-in-gaza/0000018f-6ba7-d0ae-adef-ebff68c90000</link><description>去年以色列阵亡者名单中新增了 826 名以色列士兵和其他安全部队成员，以及 834 名恐怖袭击受害者</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 08:40:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-memorial-day-kicks-off-amid-war-in-gaza/0000018f-6ba7-d0ae-adef-ebff68c90000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大航空将飞往以色列的航班暂停期限延长至八月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/air-canada-extends-suspension-of-flights-to-israel-until-august/0000018f-6b8d-d0ae-adef-ebdd1d110000</link><description>这家总部位于蒙特利尔的航空公司表示，要到 8 月 6 日才会恢复飞往特拉维夫的航班</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 07:00:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/air-canada-extends-suspension-of-flights-to-israel-until-august/0000018f-6b8d-d0ae-adef-ebdd1d110000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/0000018f-6b74-de93-a1af-7f7c5b9c0000</link><description>参谋军士。莫迪因居民纳哈尔旅的阿里尔·齐姆 (Ariel Tsym) 在加沙 Zeitoun 社区的战斗行动中身亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 06:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-strip-combat/0000018f-6b74-de93-a1af-7f7c5b9c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布贾巴利亚行动开始；加沙边境附近响起警笛声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article-live/30-arrested-detained-in-tel-aviv-protests-calling-for-hostages-release/0000018f-6aae-d4be-abcf-6bef0ce20000</link><description>英国外交大臣卡梅伦表示，对以色列实施武器禁运“不会是明智之举” ■ 身份不明的肇事者纵火焚烧约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦空屋 ■ 加沙报道称以色列国防军在贾巴利亚与哈马斯成员交战 ■ 阿什凯隆的家遭到火箭弹直接袭击;三人轻伤 ■ 据报道，美国向以色列提供情报，以换取避免拉法的大规模入侵</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 03:46:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article-live/30-arrested-detained-in-tel-aviv-protests-calling-for-hostages-release/0000018f-6aae-d4be-abcf-6bef0ce20000</guid></item><item><title>尽管与哈马斯在协议上存在分歧，但以色列不会退出人质谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-isnt-leaving-talks-cannot-confirm-status-of-hostage-in-new-hamas-video/0000018f-694b-d9a0-a38f-ed6f9bda0000</link><description>以色列上周在与卡塔尔和埃及调解人的会谈中表达了对哈马斯提议的保留</description><pubDate>Sun, 12 May 2024 03:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-isnt-leaving-talks-cannot-confirm-status-of-hostage-in-new-hamas-video/0000018f-694b-d9a0-a38f-ed6f9bda0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯播放以色列在加沙被扣为人质的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-of-israeli-held-hostage-in-gaza-captivity/0000018f-68a1-ddc4-a79f-7ca9552e0000</link><description>以色列军方认为 Nadav Poplewell 的视频很可能是过时的，他的兄弟于 10 月 7 日被杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 17:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/hamas-airs-video-of-israeli-held-hostage-in-gaza-captivity/0000018f-68a1-ddc4-a79f-7ca9552e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数万人抗议政府，警方与人质家人发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/police-clash-with-hostages-families-as-tens-of-thousands-protest-govt-across-israel/0000018f-6820-de93-a1af-7c28f1580000</link><description>“内塔尼亚胡正在带领以色列国彻底失败。埃纳夫·赞高克（Einav Zangauker）的儿子马坦（Matan）被关押在加沙，他呼吁以色列部长们停止合作，推翻政府，拯救人质和国家。</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 17:20:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/police-clash-with-hostages-families-as-tens-of-thousands-protest-govt-across-israel/0000018f-6820-de93-a1af-7c28f1580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 218 天：以色列国防军称 30 万人从拉法撤离至人道主义区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-day-218-idf-says-300-000-evacuated-from-rafah-to-humanitarian-zone/0000018f-6890-d284-adaf-7cfc7dce0000</link><description>以色列国防军：30 万人从加沙拉法撤离 ■ 拜登政府：“合理评估”以色列在“不符合”国际人道主义法的情况下使用了美国提供的武器，但没有给出结论性声明，称缺乏核实事件的信息 ■ 哈马斯的言论以色列人质视频 ■ 南非要求国际法院下令以色列从拉法撤军 ■ 战争进入 218 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 17:19:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-day-218-idf-says-300-000-evacuated-from-rafah-to-humanitarian-zone/0000018f-6890-d284-adaf-7cfc7dce0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的欧洲歌唱大赛选手在一片嘲笑声和欢呼声中获得第五名；马尔默数千人抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/eurovision-reaches-its-grand-final-as-gaza-war-tensions-steal-the-spotlight/0000018f-683a-de93-a1af-7c3afe010000</link><description>数千人在马尔默游行，抗议以色列歌手伊登·戈兰的参与并要求加沙停火；警方驱散了场馆外的数十名抗议者；在芬兰，数十名抗议者冲进公共广播公司总部，要求其因以色列的参与而退出歌曲比赛</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 15:56:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/eurovision-reaches-its-grand-final-as-gaza-war-tensions-steal-the-spotlight/0000018f-683a-de93-a1af-7c3afe010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队返回贾巴利亚，指责哈马斯重组缺乏外交程序</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-prepares-for-north-gaza-combat-accuses-hamas-regrouping-on-lack-of-diplomatic-process/0000018f-67df-d9a0-a38f-efff88f30000</link><description>以色列军队正在加沙城北部的贾巴利亚做好战斗准备，去年 12 月，以色列声称哈马斯营已清除该地区。 15万居民被号召南下疏散</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 14:21:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-prepares-for-north-gaza-combat-accuses-hamas-regrouping-on-lack-of-diplomatic-process/0000018f-67df-d9a0-a38f-efff88f30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，在以色列行动之前，有30万人从加沙南部的拉法撤离到人道主义区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-300-000-people-evacuated-rafah-to-humanitarian-zone-ahead-of-israeli-operation/0000018f-66a6-de93-a1af-7eae4ee70000</link><description>以色列国防军表示摧毁了哈马斯在加沙北部的军事能力几个月后，以色列军队正在重新部署到该地区，以遏制哈马斯营的重组。军队还宣布对加沙南部拉法更多地区下达疏散令</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 09:01:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-300-000-people-evacuated-rafah-to-humanitarian-zone-ahead-of-israeli-operation/0000018f-66a6-de93-a1af-7eae4ee70000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军士兵在加沙北部战斗中丧生；以色列对加沙北部发动猛烈轰炸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article-live/france-demands-halting-rafah-op-u-s-hints-at-israels-violations-of-intel-law-in-gaza/0000018f-6570-d284-adaf-757ce3af0000</link><description>德国肖尔茨警告说，对拉法发动地面攻击是不负责任的行为 ■ Alqahera News 报道，埃及拒绝与以色列协调援助物资从拉法过境点进入 ■ 哈马斯发布了以色列人质纳达夫·波普尔韦尔 (Nadav Poplewell) 的视频 ■ 以色列国防军向加沙北部的贾巴利亚部署部队，称哈马斯已经在该地区进行重组 ■ 以色列国防军称 30 万加沙人已撤离拉法</description><pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2024 02:42:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-11/ty-article-live/france-demands-halting-rafah-op-u-s-hints-at-israels-violations-of-intel-law-in-gaza/0000018f-6570-d284-adaf-757ce3af0000</guid></item></channel></rss>